data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Killeen. This beautifully designed property blends modern elegance with unparalleled comfort, creating the perfect space. Nestled in a peaceful neighborhood, this home offers convenience, close to schools, shopping, dining, and entertainment options.This home boasts energy-efficient features, including brand new windows and solar panels. Say goodbye to high electricity bills and embrace the future of sustainable living. The solar panel system in this home is fully operational and primed to cut your energy costs. (Home priced to pay off solar/ windows at closing) Enjoy the satisfaction of reducing your carbon footprint while accessing the long-term savings that solar energy provides. We can't wait for you to see this home in person and envision the possibilities it offers.
